<section id="approach" class="py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 border-t border-border">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <p class="font-mono text-accent text-sm mb-3 tracking-widest uppercase">Engineering Approach</p>
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">
      How I think about building things.
